# {{label|en|figuratively}} One can expect dire outcomes from any vice; {{non-gloss definition|used to convey a sense that [[poetic justice]] is inevitable}}.
# {{label|en|figuratively}} The means of one's [[success]] can become the means of one's [[downfall]].
